# --- Secrets: never commit credentials, keys, or live secret material ---
# Anything under a secrets/ directory is ignored, EXCEPT its README placeholder.
# Keep real secrets in a proper vault (e.g., HashiCorp Vault, Ansible Vault,
# Windows Credential Manager) — this repo is for declarative plans, not secrets.
**/secrets/*
!**/secrets/README.md

# Common credential / key file patterns, wherever they appear
*.pem
*.key
*.pfx
*.p12
*.kdbx
*_rsa
*_ed25519
.env
*.env
credentials*
*secret*.yml
*secret*.yaml
vault-password*

# OS / editor noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~
.idea/
.vscode/
